  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About Ice Slider</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Ice Slider</strong> is a game by Shining Watermelon Studios where you play as a hiker named Rob who enters Icy Cave. A cave with a Gauntlet of Ice Puzzles, in which he has to complete to exit. Play as Rob as he goes through this gauntlet of puzzles. Each Level contains new challenges using Walls and other obstacles like Dirt, which stops you in your tracks, Move Tiles, which spin you in their specified direction, and Rotate Tiles, which spin you randomly based on their current direction. The game contains 20 base game levels for you to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About Ice Slider</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Ice Slider</strong> is a game by Shining Watermelon Studios where you play as a hiker named Rob who enters Icy Cave. A cave with a Gauntlet of Ice Puzzles, in which he has to complete to exit. Play as Rob as he goes through this gauntlet of puzzles. Each Level contains new challenges using Walls and other obstacles like Dirt, which stops you in your tracks, Move Tiles, which spin you in their specified direction, and Rotate Tiles, which spin you randomly based on their current direction. The game contains 20 base game levels for you to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
